Package: compbench
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, btrfs-progs, xz-utils, gdisk, curl
Description: Btrfs transparent compression benchmark
 Benchmarks Btrfs compression algorithms (zstd, lzo) by measuring read/write
 throughput, compression ratio, CPU usage, and disk I/O using direct
 kernel interfaces. No text parsing of external tool output.
